---

<Layout title="AETHERIA | Colección Cuero" lang="es" description="Descubra la Colección Cuero de AETHERIA Guatemala. Texturas crudas de alquitrán de abedul, oud ahumado y ante. Elegancia primigenia en alta perfumería de lujo.">
  <header
    data-mobile-nav
    class="sticky top-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center h-[100px] px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-outline-variant"
  >
    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-8">
      <a
        class="font-display-xl text-headline-md tracking-widest text-primary"
        href="/"
      >AETHERIA</a>
      <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-10">
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary border-b border-primary pb-1 transition-colors duration-300"
          href="/collections"
        >Colecciones</a>
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >Notas Olfativas</a>
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >El Archivo</a>
        <a
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
          href="#"
        >Bespoke</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">search</span>
      </button>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">shopping_bag</span>
      </button>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
      </button>
      <button class="hamburger md:hidden touch-target" data-toggle-mobile aria-label="Menú">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="mobile-drawer" data-mobile-drawer>
    <a href="/collections" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Colecciones</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Notas Olfativas</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">El Archivo</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Bespoke</a>
    <hr class="border-outline-variant my-4" />
    <a href="/" class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-overlay" data-mobile-overlay></div>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section
      class="relative w-full min-h-screen md:h-[870px] flex items-center px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop overflow-hidden fade-in"
    >
      <div class="z-10 w-full grid grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-start fade-in">
          <span
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mb-4"
          >EL EDITORIAL OLFATIVO</span>
          <h1 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-6 leading-tight">
            Colección Cuero
          </h1>
          <p
            class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-md mb-10"
          >
            Una exploración de elegancia primigenia. Texturas crudas de alquitrán
            de abedul, tabaco ahumado y la suavidad íntima del ante reimaginadas
            a través de un lente de minimalismo de alto lujo.
          </p>
          <button
            class="px-10 py-4 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest hover:bg-surface-tint transition-all duration-500"
          >
            DESCUBRIR LA GAMA
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex col-span-7 justify-end relative h-full">
          <div class="w-[85%] h-[90%] bg-surface-container overflow-hidden group">
            <div
              class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105"
              style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCWKc3KIYmMDV8BQuBOBnvv2ijheWzynNdvsriaakKWiJcKDgVV06qD3T4nKhtr2v7iJDLv3Z5DfNR-2xyd9N4HoVb273TzH8zcxi9JLPjF3h6PaynMU6SqHTlcVhF7e0o-AkX3ShHaxEFrqK6Bxn5h7zNQI_VoYWiEujnEs4tAIafjFQ81a2Oa26RLQtWXtTwJOf0YLqPkpZ_MgyIzs7bbk9Ou26_ciFRLsUtl3rQHGaLAS4QKdV_Y0YSN4fdbKPVzWt8RrEHN4M_7')"
            ></div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -left-12 bottom-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-6"
          >
            <span
              class="text-vertical font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant"
            >TEMPORADA 01 / CUERO</span>
            <div class="w-px h-24 bg-outline-variant"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Signature Notes -->
    <section
      class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop border-y border-outline-variant/30 fade-in"
    >
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
          >NOTA PRIMARIA</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">Alquitrán de Abedul</h3>
          <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
            El corazón ahumado del acorde de cuero.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
          >TEXTURA</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">Oud Ahumado</h3>
          <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
            Añadiendo profundidad y complejidad resinosa.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
          >ACABADO</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">Ante</h3>
          <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
            Un aroma aterciopelado que perdura como la piel.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
          >INTENSIDAD</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">Tabaco</h3>
          <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
            Dulce, terroso y audaz sin disculpas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Product Grid -->
    <section class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop fade-in">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-20">
        <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md">El Archivo</h2>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps border border-outline px-6 py-2 hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all"
          >FILTRAR</button>
          <button
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps border border-outline px-6 py-2 hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all"
          >ORDENAR POR</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-gutter gap-y-16 md:gap-y-section-gap"
      >
        {products.map((product) => (
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <div
              class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container overflow-hidden mb-8 relative"
            >
              <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
              ></div>
              <div
                class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                style={`background-image: url('${product.img}')`}
              ></div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span
                class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
              >{product.badge}</span>
              <h3
                class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm uppercase tracking-widest"
              >
                {product.name}
              </h3>
              <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                {product.price}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Newsletter -->
    <section
      class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface-container-low text-center fade-in"
    >
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
        <span
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mb-6"
        >ACCESO EXCLUSIVO</span>
        <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-8">
          Únase al Archivo
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-10">
          Reciba invitaciones a lanzamientos de colecciones privadas y consultas
          de aromas personalizadas.
        </p>
        <div class="w-full flex border-b border-primary max-w-md">
          <input
            class="flex-1 bg-transparent border-none py-3 font-label-caps text-label-caps focus:ring-0 placeholder:text-on-surface-variant/50"
            placeholder="DIRECCIÓN DE CORREO"
            type="email"
          />
          <button
            class="px-6 py-3 font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest"
          >
            SUSCRIBIRSE
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer
    class="w-full py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-unit border-t border-outline-variant"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-4">
      <span
        class="font-display-xl text-headline-sm tracking-widest text-primary"
      >AETHERIA</span>
      <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant">
        © 2026 AETHERIA. TODOS LOS DERECHOS RESERVADOS.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-2 mt-8 md:mt-0">
      <span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary mb-2"
      >GUATEMALA</span>
      <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
        Avenida Reforma 12-01, Zona 10, Ciudad de Guatemala
      </p>
      <p class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant">
        +502 2300 0000
      </p>
      <a
        class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="mailto:info@aetheria.com"
      >info@aetheria.com</a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-10 mt-8 md:mt-0">
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Privacidad</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Términos</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Envíos</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Contacto</a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-6 mt-8 md:mt-0">
      <a
        class="w-10 h-10 border border-outline-variant rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all duration-300"
        href="#"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-[18px]">share</span>
      </a>
      <a
        class="w-10 h-10 border border-outline-variant rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all duration-300"
        href="#"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-[18px]">mail</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
